<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you&#8217;ve gathered the most critical documents, the only place you need to go now is to a convenient bank branch near you. But remember: Each bank, even each branch, may have its own order. Therefore, you can make the process easier by calling the branch before you go and asking &#8220;I am a foreign student, I want to open an account. Which documents are required?&#8221;</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Don&#8217;t be afraid to take the first step. Student life in Turkey is nice, but much more practical if you have a bank account!</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-08-26T10:31:35Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:45:13Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/opening-a-bank-account-for-international-students-in-turkey.webp","alt":"An international student opening a bank account at a branch in Turkey.","title":"opening-a-bank-account-for-international-students-in-turkey"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'turkey-student-bank-account-opening' );
