<div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height: 23px;" aria-hidden="true"> </div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" />
<h2 class="wp-block-spacer" style="height: 23px;" aria-hidden="true">What Advantages Are Waiting For You With University Industry Cooperation?</h2>
<h2 id="universite-sanayi-isbirligi-ile-what-advantages-are-waiting-for-you" class="wp-block-heading"> </h2>


<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="work-experience-internship-and-career-paths">Work Experience, Internship and Career Paths</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The biggest advantage of these collaborations? Work experience. By getting involved in University-Industry projects, students make a significant contribution to their CVs before they graduate. Project-based internships, part-time R&amp;D assignments, even full-time job offers&#8230; All these are much closer to you when you are part of these collaborations.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You don&#8217;t need to fight for an internship; if you take part in the project, you are already considered to have done an internship. Some companies even hire these students before they graduate.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="entrepreneurship-opportunities-and-investor-support">Entrepreneurship Opportunities and Investor Support</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkey&#8217;s technoparks and entrepreneurship centers offer students not only jobs but also the opportunity to start their own businesses as part of University-Industry cooperation. Projects developed with R&amp;D support are commercialized by obtaining patents. In this process, both your teachers and investors are working with you.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you have a business idea but no capital, technopark incubation programs or startup support such as TUBITAK 1512 can pave the way.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="a-step-to-the-future-with-university-industry-cooperation">A Step to the Future with University Industry Cooperation</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="scholarship-calendar-and-important-application-dates-in-turkey">Scholarship Calendar and Important Application Dates in Turkey</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Applications for University-Industry cooperation programs are usually opened periodically. TUBITAK publishes call announcements every year in <strong>January, May and September</strong>. Each call has its own application form, project description and evaluation schedule.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-to-do-if-you-dont-win-a-scholarship">What to do if you don&#8217;t win a scholarship</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">It is not always possible to be accepted for scholarship applications. But that doesn&#8217;t mean your dreams are over in Turkey. You can continue your education and gain experience with alternative income methods:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>You can work part-time jobs.</li>



<li>You can increase your income by teaching online.</li>



<li>You can earn digital income by producing freelance content.</li>
</ul>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="shaping-your-future-is-in-your-hands">Shaping Your Future is in Your Hands</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In Turkey, University-Industry cooperation is not just a concept. A system that really works, earns money for the student, offers experience and opens the doors to jobs after graduation. If you have scientific curiosity, want to take part in real projects and want to turn your education into a career, now is the time to take the step.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-08-26T10:35:47Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:45:08Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/kling_20250806_Text_to_Image_A_modern_u_4788_1.png","alt":"An illustrated industrial scene with factories, gears, and machinery symbolizing technological development.","title":"kling_20250806_Text_to_Image_A_modern_u_4788_1"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'university-industry-cooperation-scholarships' );
