ng you need to know about national and international competition scholarships in Turkey! Apply now and get one step closer to your dream education.","name":"National and International Competition Scholarships","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/national-international-competition-scholarships/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/national-international-competition-scholarships/#webpage"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/national-and-international-competition-scholarships-in-turkiye.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/national-international-competition-scholarships/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<h2 id="contest-scholarships-what-are-and-how-does-it-work" class="wp-block-heading">What are Contest Scholarships and How Do They Work?</h2>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Scholarships offer a vital opportunity for many students who want to study in Turkey. Among these, especially <strong>international competition scholarships</strong> stand out in terms of both financial support and academic prestige. So what exactly are these scholarships?</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="who-are-these-scholarships-intended-for">Who are these scholarships intended for?</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>High school seniors</li>



<li>Bachelor&#8217;s degree candidates and students</li>



<li>Master&#8217;s/PhD students</li>



<li>Foreign nationals wishing to study in Turkey</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>International competition scholarships</strong> aim to promote cultural exchange, especially for foreign students, while adding value to Turkey&#8217;s academic world.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="national-competition-scholarships-in-turkey-major-options">National Competition Scholarships in Turkey: Major Options</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In Turkey, many state institutions and private foundations offer scholarships to students participating in national competitions. These scholarships are mainly for Turkish citizens, but some are also open to foreign students.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The table below lists some of the most important <strong>national competition scholarships</strong> in Turkey and the institutions that provide them:</p>


<figure class="wp-block-table">
<table class="has-fixed-layout">
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Institution Name</th>
<th>Scholarship Type</th>
<th>Who Can Apply</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>TUBITAK</td>
<td>Science Competitions Scholarship</td>
<td>High school and university students</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Turkish Academy of Sciences</td>
<td>Academic Achievement Scholarships</td>
<td>University students</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</figure>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">These scholarships are usually awarded automatically or by application to award-winning students. The requirements for international students are usually specified in the details of the scholarship. But beware: some competitions are conducted only in Turkish.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="open-competition-scholarships-for-international-students">Open Competition Scholarships for International Students</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Here we come to the most crucial part: <strong>international competition scholarships</strong> are a serious opportunity for foreign students who want to study in Turkey. These scholarships are awarded not only by application but also by placing in certain competitions. Universities, embassies and international foundations in Turkey often sponsor such scholarships.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="sample-competitions">Sample Competitions:</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Turkish Speaking Competitions (sponsored by YTB)</li>



<li>Engineering Project Competitions (organized by some universities)</li>



<li>International High School Project Competitions (organizations such as INSPO, OKSEF)</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Most of these types of scholarships can be in the form of full scholarships or dormitory+tuition fees. Below you can see the most common types of <strong>international competition scholarships</strong> offered in Turkey:</p>


<figure class="wp-block-table">
<table class="has-fixed-layout">
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Scholarship Type</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Language and Culture Scholarships</td>
<td>Granted to students who speak Turkish</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>STEM Project Competition Scholarships</td>
<td>Granted to those who rank in science/art projects</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>International Writing Competitions</td>
<td>Essay, Participate with texts such as articles, stories</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</figure>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You can find detailed and up-to-date announcements about these scholarships via <a class="" href="https://www.ytb.gov.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Presidency for Turks Abroad and Related Communities</a>.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Here is the most important tip: Analyze the contest topic and jury criteria well before applying. Because &#8220;participating is not enough, you have to win.&#8221; Competition is increasing every year, especially for <strong>international competition scholarships</strong>.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="tips-to-win-a-scholarship-things-to-consider-in-the-application-process">Tips to Win a Scholarship: Things to Consider in the Application Process</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">&#8220;Winning a scholarship is not just a matter of filling out a form,&#8221; I was told by many people who agreed with me. In particular, the application process for <strong>international competition scholarships</strong> requires both attention and strategy.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="here-are-some-tips-you-might-find-useful">Here are some tips you might find useful:</h3>



<ol class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Pre-Competition Preparation</strong></li>



<li><strong>Prepare Your Documents Perfectly</strong></li>



<li><strong>Spirit Your Motivation Letter</strong></li>
</ol>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">It can also be very helpful to get mentor support to increase your chances of winning the scholarship. Remember, many students will apply for the same <strong>international competition scholarships</strong> as you. That&#8217;s why authenticity and quality are everything.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="scholarships-and-visa-process-what-you-should-pay-attention-to">Scholarships and Visa Process: What You Should Pay Attention To</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>When you win international competition scholarships</strong>, your work is not 100% done. You need a student visa to come to Turkey. This process may vary depending on the type of scholarship.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="documents-required-for-visa-application">Documents Required for Visa Application:</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Certificate of scholarship attainment (original and signed)</li>



<li>Acceptance letter</li>



<li>Passport and biometric photo</li>



<li>Information of the sponsoring organization in Turkey</li>



<li>Documents showing accommodation and financial status</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The consulates of the Republic of Turkey usually give priority treatment to students who win <strong>international competition scholarships</strong>. However, each country has a different procedure. So it is very important to check the details on the <a>official consular website</a>.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">As a scholarship student, you also have obligations after you get a visa. For example, our article <a>Responsibilities and Expectations After Scholarship in Turkey</a> explains this topic in detail. Each type of scholarship may have different rules, such as restrictions on the duration of study or post-graduation work.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="start-now-to-reach-your-dream-education">Start Now to Reach Your Dream Education</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>International competition scholarships</strong> are not just financial support; they are a chain of opportunities. Studying in a culturally and academically rich country like Turkey can change your life completely.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In this article, I have covered many points, from the application process to real stories. Now I just need one step from you:<br><strong>Apply. Follow the calendars. Believe in yourself.</strong></p>', "wp_published_at" = '2025-08-26T10:36:10Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2026-03-15T18:45:06Z', "featured_image" = '{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/national-and-international-competition-scholarships-in-turkiye.webp","alt":"A trophy and medal on a stage representing academic and competition success.","title":"national-and-international-competition-scholarships-in-turkiye"}' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'national-international-competition-scholarships';
