<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The consulates of the Republic of Turkey usually give priority treatment to students who win <strong>international competition scholarships</strong>. However, each country has a different procedure. So it is very important to check the details on the <a>official consular website</a>.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">As a scholarship student, you also have obligations after you get a visa. For example, our article <a>Responsibilities and Expectations After Scholarship in Turkey</a> explains this topic in detail. Each type of scholarship may have different rules, such as restrictions on the duration of study or post-graduation work.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="start-now-to-reach-your-dream-education">Start Now to Reach Your Dream Education</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>International competition scholarships</strong> are not just financial support; they are a chain of opportunities. Studying in a culturally and academically rich country like Turkey can change your life completely.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In this article, I have covered many points, from the application process to real stories. Now I just need one step from you:<br><strong>Apply. Follow the calendars. Believe in yourself.</strong></p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-08-26T10:36:10Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:45:06Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/national-and-international-competition-scholarships-in-turkiye.webp","alt":"A trophy and medal on a stage representing academic and competition success.","title":"national-and-international-competition-scholarships-in-turkiye"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'national-international-competition-scholarships' );
