</div></figure>


<div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height: 55px;" aria-hidden="true"> </div>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you want to study mechanical engineering and gain both theoretical knowledge and real-world experience, Özyeğin University can offer you more than you think. Located in Çekmeköy, in the east of Istanbul, this university stands out with its innovative approach to engineering.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">When I first saw the campus, I was a bit surprised, because it was very different from the classic university buildings. Modern, simple and green&#8230; But you really feel the difference in education. So is this program for you? Let&#8217;s take a look at the details.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="ozyegin-university-foreign-student-fees-2025-2026">Ozyegin University Foreign Student Fees 2025-2026</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Özyeğin University offers various scholarship opportunities for foreign students. Here is the wage table for 2025-2026:</p>


<figure class="wp-block-table">
<table class="has-fixed-layout">
<thead>
<tr>
<tr>
<th><strong>Scholarship Type</strong></th>
<th><strong>Annual Fee (USD)</strong></th>
</th>
<th><strong>Description</strong></th>
</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><strong>Full Scholarship</strong></td>
<td>0</td>
<td>The education is completely free of charge. Food/housing scholarship can also be added.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>50% Scholarship</strong></td>
<td>11,000</td>
<td>Half the normal fee.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>Fee</strong></td>
<td>22,000</td>
<td>Full annual fee for non-scholarship students.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</figure>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In addition, entrance scholarships can be awarded by faculty members based on academic achievement during the application process. For details, you can check <a href="https://admissions.ozyegin.edu.tr/tr/ucretler-ve-burslar" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Scholarship Terms and Conditions</a>.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="2024-mechanical-engineering-placement-scores">2024 Mechanical Engineering Placement Scores</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">According to the 2024 placement results, Özyeğin University Mechanical Engineering department accepted students with very high rankings. Current quota and score details are as follows:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-table"><table class="has-fixed-layout"><thead><tr><th><strong>Scholarship Type</strong></th><th><strong>2024 Quota</strong></th><th><strong>2024 Min. Score</strong></th><th><strong>2024 Max. Score</strong></th><th><strong>2024 Min. Ranking</strong></th><th><strong>2024 Max. Ranking</strong></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Full Scholarship</td><td>9</td><td>504.37918</td><td>516.66683</td><td>8,917</td><td>5,139</td></tr><tr><td>50% Scholarship</td><td>42</td><td>375.12672</td><td>482.99644</td><td>111,348</td><td>18,186</td></tr><tr><td>Paid (No Scholarship)</td><td>17</td><td>291.34439</td><td>371.31270</td><td>295,285</td><td>116,285</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">This data is taken from <strong>Ozyegin University&#8217;s official website</strong>.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="mechanical-engineering-syllabus-what-you-will-learn">Mechanical Engineering Syllabus: What You Will Learn</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Mechanical engineering may sound only &#8220;technical&#8221;, but Ozyegin University breaks this perception. There is a program full of both basic engineering courses and practical applications.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>1st and 2nd Year (Basic Information)</strong></p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Physics, Chemistry, Mathematics</li>



<li>Statics, Thermodynamics, Materials Science</li>



<li>Computer Aided Design (CAD)</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>3rd and 4th Year (Practice and Specialization)</strong></p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Fluid Mechanics, Heat Transfer</li>



<li>Automation Systems</li>



<li>Graduation Project and Internships</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">You have the chance to actually use the equipment in the lab classes. You can also find information about interaction and joint projects with other engineering departments on the <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/ozyegin-muhendislik-fakultesi/" data-type="post" data-id="3048">Özyeğin University Faculty of Engineering</a> page.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="ozyegin-university-campus-and-location-guide">Ozyegin University Campus and Location Guide</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Located in Çekmeköy, the campus is surrounded by nature. It is also very accessible in terms of transportation:</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Transportation Guide:</strong></p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Metro:</strong> M5 Üsküdar-Çekmeköy line</li>



<li><strong>Buses:</strong> Lines like 522, 11R and 14Ş</li>



<li><strong>Service:</strong> University shuttle services</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The Entrepreneurship Center, sports fields, modern library and dormitories on campus meet the needs of students. For details, check out our <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/ozyegin-kampus-konum/" data-type="post" data-id="3055">guide to university life</a>.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="about-mechanical-engineering-what-is-our-goal">About Mechanical Engineering: What is our goal?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The aim of the Department of Mechanical Engineering at Ozyegin University is not only to impart technical knowledge, but also to train engineers who are researchers, entrepreneurs and solution-oriented. The department aims to produce graduates who will have a say in the design of systems, devices and production processes, and who can directly contribute to the industry.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Having a solid technical and scientific background with a good command of current technologies is considered commonplace in this department. What makes the real difference is that the student is trained as a producer, not just a learner. The academic team makes this possible with projects open to <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/universite-sanayi-isbirligi-burslari/" data-type="post" data-id="3161">university-industry cooperation</a>.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The department has also received <strong>MÜDEK accreditation</strong> and has international quality approval among engineering programs in Turkey. The language of instruction is English and the program duration is 4 years.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For more information, check out the <a href="https://www.ozyegin.edu.tr/pdfviewer/muhendislik-2023-2024.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">chapter brochure</a> or the official website.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-do-graduates-do-career-opportunities">What do graduates do? Career Opportunities</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">For mechanical engineering graduates, graduation is actually the beginning of the real journey. Students graduating from Özyeğin University are building solid careers in many sectors both in Turkey and abroad. The applied education model offered by the university, the projects that establish close contact with the industry and the strong career office play a major role in this.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="rampd-production-and-engineering-services">R&amp;D, Production and Engineering Services</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Many graduates work in large industrial organizations in areas such as R&amp;D (Research and Development), production planning or quality control. These include Turkey&#8217;s leading engineering companies such as ASELSAN, Roketsan, Arçelik, Ford Otosan and TEI. Automotive, defense industry and durable consumer goods sectors are among the most preferred areas.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>True graduate stories</strong> usually start like this: Thanks to internships during university, it is not rare to enter the sector and receive job offers before graduation.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="entrepreneurship-and-self-employment">Entrepreneurship and Self-Employment</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Mechanical engineering doesn&#8217;t always mean &#8220;working for someone else&#8221;. Thanks to Özyeğin University&#8217;s Entrepreneurship Center and support programs, some students are implementing their own ideas even before they graduate. It is possible to come across start-ups in different fields, from those that produce spare parts with 3D printers to start-ups working on sustainable energy systems.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="academic-career-and-research">Academic Career and Research</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Of course, some graduates prefer to take the academic route. There are also those who work as research assistants at universities and continue their master&#8217;s and PhD programs in Turkey. If you are someone who wants to do research in mechanical engineering, Özyeğin&#8217;s laboratory infrastructure and publication support can motivate you on this path.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="studying-mechanical-engineering-at-ozyeginde">To Study Mechanical Engineering in Ozyegin</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Mechanical engineering is a promising but demanding field. Özyeğin University is a place that can offer you a real infrastructure on this path. If you want to improve yourself with both academic and practical training, now is the time to start researching.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-07-23T08:45:56Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:52:34Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ozyegin-university-mechanical-engineering.webp","alt":"Ozyegin university mechanical engineering","title":"ozyegin-university-mechanical-engineering"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'ozyegin-university-of-mechanical-engineering' );
