:"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/blockchain-and-cryptocurrency-scholarships-in-turkiye.webp","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/blockchain-and-cryptocurrency-scholarships-in-turkiye.webp","width":"2336","height":"1760","caption":"A student analyzing blockchain data on a laptop, with cryptocurrency icons in the background.","inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/turkey-cryptocurrency-scholarships/#webpage","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/turkey-cryptocurrency-scholarships/","name":"Cryptocurrency and Blockchain Scholarships","datePublished":"2025-08-26T13:46:15+03:00","dateModified":"2026-03-15T21:44:58+03:00","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#website"},"primaryImageOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/blockchain-and-cryptocurrency-scholarships-in-turkiye.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Person","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","caption":"Murat","inLanguage":"en-US"}},{"headline":"Cryptocurrency and Blockchain Scholarships","description":"Cryptocurrency scholarships, blockchain-powered education, and application guides for international students who want to study in Turkey. Discover now!","datePublished":"2025-08-26T13:46:15+03:00","dateModified":"2026-03-15T21:44:58+03:00","keywords":"Cryptocurrency","image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/blockchain-and-cryptocurrency-scholarships-in-turkiye.webp"},"author":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat"},"@type":"BlogPosting","name":"Cryptocurrency and Blockchain Scholarships","articleSection":"Scholarships and Funding","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/turkey-cryptocurrency-scholarships/#schema-17352","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/turkey-cryptocurrency-scholarships/#webpage"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/turkey-cryptocurrency-scholarships/#webpage"}},{"@type":"VideoObject","name":"Cryptocurrency and Blockchain Scholarships","description":"Enjoy the videos and music you love, upload original content, and share it all with friends, family, and the world on YouTube.","uploadDate":"2025-08-26T13:46:15+03:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/blockchain-and-cryptocurrency-scholarships-in-turkiye.webp","embedUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries","isFamilyFriendly":"True","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/turkey-cryptocurrency-scholarships/#schema-17353","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/turkey-cryptocurrency-scholarships/#webpage"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/turkey-cryptocurrency-scholarships/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="what-is-cryptocurrency-and-blockchain">What is Cryptocurrency and Blockchain?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Cryptocurrency and blockchain are two of the most talked about concepts in today&#8217;s digital world. Especially for international students who grow up intertwined with technology, knowing these concepts is not just a curiosity; it has become almost a necessity.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="basic-structure-of-blockchain-technology">Basic Structure of Blockchain Technology</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Blockchain is a technology that stores data transparently and securely on a decentralized network. In this system, information is written in blocks in chains and these blocks are stored without being changed. In other words, think of a transparent digital ledger that cannot be copied or erased. This structure has started to be used not only in finance but also in many other fields such as education and health.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="how-cryptocurrency-works-and-where-to-use-it">How Cryptocurrency Works and Where to Use It?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Cryptocurrency is a product of this blockchain system. You&#8217;ve probably heard of names like Bitcoin and Ethereum. Unlike state-backed currencies, these are decentralized digital currencies, meaning they are not controlled by any government or bank. </p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Some universities in Turkey are setting up cryptocurrency labs to teach their students about them. These digital assets, which are used as both investment and payment methods, are also used to fund some educational scholarships.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="new-era-in-education-with-cryptocurrency-technology">New Era in Education with Cryptocurrency Technology</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Education is no longer limited to the classroom. Thanks to this technology, students can both receive scholarships and access educational content through decentralized networks. In particular, the next generation internet system, known as Web3, is at the heart of this change.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="web3-and-decentralization-in-education">Web3 and Decentralization in Education</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Web3 offers a system where users have more say on the internet. Traditional education platforms are being replaced by blockchain-supported platforms. Students can receive their achievements in the form of NFTs (like digital certificates). Some private institutions in Turkey have already started this transition. This transition is especially fast in departments such as software, game design and digital arts.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="scholarship-models-funded-by-cryptocurrency">Scholarship Models Funded by Cryptocurrency</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">While traditional scholarships are usually provided by universities or government agencies, cryptocurrency-funded scholarships offer a more innovative approach. For example, some blockchain projects or DAOs (Decentralized Autonomous Organizations) pay successful students in cryptocurrency.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="blockchain-and-cryptocurrency-scholarships-in-turkey">Blockchain and Cryptocurrency Scholarships in Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In recent years, universities in Turkey have also attached great importance to cryptocurrency and blockchain education. This offers serious opportunities for international students. Especially scholarships supported by private universities and large technology companies stand out.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="metaverse-scholarship-halic-universitys-pioneering-step">Metaverse Scholarship &#8211; Halic University&#8217;s Pioneering Step</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Starting a Metaverse-themed scholarship program for the first time in Turkey, Haliç University supports students studying in departments such as Blockchain, Software, Game Design and Digital Arts. The aim of this scholarship is to raise individuals who are ready for the digital world of the future. Scholarships are usually provided to students with amounts ranging from 250 to 500 USD. Haliç University also offers internship and research opportunities to its students with METAVERSE R&amp;D Center.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><a href="https://halic.edu.tr/tr/s-universitemiz/basinBultenleri/halic-universitesi-metaverse-bursu-bb.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source PDF &#8211; Haliç University Official Publication</a></p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="binance-charity-and-web3-education-scholarships">Binance Charity and Web3 Education Scholarships</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Binance Charity, Binance&#8217;s charity organization, provides scholarships to young people who want to pursue a career in Web3. Partnering with some educational institutions in Turkey, this organization pays students directly with cryptocurrency. The aim is not only to support young people financially, but also to develop them into individuals who will contribute to Web3 technologies. Scholarships are usually worth USD 150-300 and include access to online courses or projects.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="universities-providing-cryptocurrency-education-in-turkey">Universities Providing Cryptocurrency Education in Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Blockchain-based education programs in Turkey are diversifying every year. Thanks to the academic investments made in this field, especially in the last five years, not only computer engineering, but also different departments such as business administration, law, graphic design have started to offer integrated education with this technology.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">This transformation is a great opportunity for foreign students who want to study in Turkey. It becomes possible to get acquainted with current technology and to draw a more competitive career path after graduation.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="blockchain-development-at-istanbul-esenyurt-university">Blockchain Development at Istanbul Esenyurt University</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><a href="https://roadtostudy.com/universiteler-istanbul-esenyurt-universitesi/">Istanbul Esenyurt University</a> is among the universities investing in technology since 2013. It draws attention with special seminars, research projects and student clubs called Blockchain Technology and Cryptocurrency. The university&#8217;s Technology and Entrepreneurship Club prepares students for the sector by organizing Blockchain Hackathons every year.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="certificates-and-programs-at-other-universities">Certificates and Programs at Other Universities</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkey&#8217;s leading universities offer a comprehensive curriculum in this field through both undergraduate and short-term certificate programs.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong>Istanbul Technical University (ITU)</strong> is offering a certificate program in English called &#8220;Blockchain and Smart Contracts&#8221;. In this program, students study advanced topics such as Ethereum, Solidity and Web3 wallet management.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<iframe loading="lazy" title="Akıllı Kontrat Geliştiriciliği Kampı Tüm Liste | İTÜ Blockchain" width="720" height="405" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLby2HXktGwN4Cof_6a8YwlMrboX8-hs73" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
</div></figure>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Some universities may reimburse part of this fee as a scholarship based on academic achievement or project proposal. While the use of cryptocurrency in education in Turkey is becoming more and more widespread, it is worth noting that <strong>some universities have started to switch to Web3-supported identity systems</strong>.</p>


<div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height: 23px;" aria-hidden="true"> </div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" />
<div class="wp-block-spacer" style="height: 24px;" aria-hidden="true"> </div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="the-application-process-what-to-do-for-cryptocurrency-scholarships">The Application Process: What to Do for Cryptocurrency Scholarships?</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Applying for cryptocurrency-focused scholarships in Turkey is not as complicated as one might think, but there are some important points to consider. Especially for foreign students, it is very important that the documents are complete and the timing of the application is very important.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="required-documents-and-online-application-systems">Required Documents and Online Application Systems</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Most cryptocurrency scholarships require the following documents:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Identity document or passport</li>



<li>Student certificate or acceptance letter</li>



<li>Letter of intent (especially motivation related to Web3)</li>



<li>Academic transcript</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Applications are mostly made through online platforms. Binance Charity accepts scholarship applications directly through its website, while universities accept applications through e-government or their student portals.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="advice-for-being-successful">Advice for Being Successful</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Success in cryptocurrency scholarships is not limited to grades. Interest in Web3, previous projects, even personal blogs or Github profiles are considered. A good letter of intent written in English can make your application process much easier.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="financial-guide-for-international-students">Financial Guide for International Students</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Studying in Turkey can be advantageous both economically and technologically. However, financial planning is essential in addition to scholarships. Although cryptocurrency scholarships provide support in this regard, it is important to think long-term.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="responsibilities-and-expectations-after-the-scholarship">Responsibilities and Expectations After the Scholarship</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Most cryptocurrency scholarships ask the student to produce volunteer activities or projects on specific topics. For example, a Web3 company offering a scholarship may require the student to develop an open source project or contribute to communities. Such obligations are clearly stated in the scholarship contract. For details, you can check our <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/burs-sonrasi-beklentiler/" data-type="post" data-id="3178">Responsibilities and Expectations After Scholarship in Turkey</a> page.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="financial-planning-after-graduation">Financial Planning After Graduation</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">There are many job opportunities in the cryptocurrency industry for students who want to stay and work in Turkey after graduation. It is possible to earn dollar-based earnings in areas such as freelance blockchain development, NFT design or Web3 marketing consultancy. However, in order to be successful in these fields, proper career planning is required. For detailed tips, you may find our content on <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/turkiye-finansal-planlama-mezunlar/" data-type="post" data-id="3184">Financial Planning After Graduation in Turkey</a> useful.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="catch-the-future-with-blockchain-scholarships">Catch the Future with Blockchain Scholarships</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you are thinking of studying in Turkey, now is the time to apply! With Metaverse scholarships, Web3-backed funding, and private university support, you can make a solid entry into the blockchain world.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Cryptocurrency is not just an investment tool; it is also an educational opportunity where you can shape your future. Turkey can literally be a starting point for international students who want to take a step in this field.</p>', "wp_published_at" = '2025-08-26T10:46:15Z', "wp_modified_at" = '2026-03-15T18:44:58Z', "featured_image" = '{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/blockchain-and-cryptocurrency-scholarships-in-turkiye.webp","alt":"A student analyzing blockchain data on a laptop, with cryptocurrency icons in the background.","title":"blockchain-and-cryptocurrency-scholarships-in-turkiye"}' WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'turkey-cryptocurrency-scholarships';
