,"name":"Road to Study - Turkey University Guide for Students","alternateName":"Road to Study in Turkey","publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/social-impact-analysis-of-scholarship-programs-in-turkey.webp","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/social-impact-analysis-of-scholarship-programs-in-turkey.webp","width":"2336","height":"1760","caption":"Two students sitting on the grass and talking, with a university building in the background.","inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/turkey-scholarships-social-impact-analysis/#webpage","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/turkey-scholarships-social-impact-analysis/","name":"Social Impact Analysis: The Power of Scholarships in Turkey","datePublished":"2025-08-26T13:49:26+03:00","dateModified":"2026-03-15T21:44:54+03:00","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#website"},"primaryImageOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/social-impact-analysis-of-scholarship-programs-in-turkey.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Person","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","caption":"Murat","inLanguage":"en-US"}},{"@type":"BlogPosting","headline":"Social Impact Analysis: The Power of Scholarships in Turkey","keywords":"Social Impact","datePublished":"2025-08-26T13:49:26+03:00","dateModified":"2026-03-15T21:44:54+03:00","articleSection":"Scholarships and Funding","author":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"description":"Discover the social impact analysis of scholarships in Turkey on international students! Academic, cultural, and social opportunities await you. Apply now!","name":"Social Impact Analysis: The Power of Scholarships in Turkey","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/turkey-scholarships-social-impact-analysis/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/turkey-scholarships-social-impact-analysis/#webpage"},"image":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/social-impact-analysis-of-scholarship-programs-in-turkey.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/turkey-scholarships-social-impact-analysis/#webpage"}}]}]}'), '$.content_html', '<p class="wp-block-paragraph">I was surprised to learn that the scholarship system in Turkey is not limited to financial support, as it also includes social services such as housing, food, transportation and even psychological support. This is the basis for social impact analysis: Education is becoming a tool of transformation, not just a diploma.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="major-institutions-and-types-of-support">Major Institutions and Types of Support</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">There are many organizations that provide scholarships for foreign students in Turkey. The most well-known ones:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Turkey Scholarships Program</strong> (<a href="https://ytb.gov.tr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YTB</a>): It offers many advantages such as full scholarship, accommodation, health insurance, monthly allowance, Turkish language education, etc.</li>



<li><strong>University Scholarships</strong>: Universities such as METU, Bogazici, Koc, Sabanci offer scholarships based on academic achievement.</li>



<li><strong>Foundation and Association Scholarships</strong>: There are organizations that support international students such as IHH, Ansar Foundation, Al-Furqan.</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="number-of-annual-scholarships">Number of Annual Scholarships</h3>


<figure class="wp-block-table">
<table class="has-fixed-layout">
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Institution Name</th>
<th>Number of Scholars per Year</th>
<th>Extra Support</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Turkey Scholarships</td>
<td>5.000+</td>
<td>Accommodation, health, language course</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>ODTU</td>
<td>500</td>
<td>Food, dormitory, transportation</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>IHH Scholarship Program</td>
<td>300</td>
<td>Book aid, counseling</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</figure>


<p class="wp-block-paragraph">These figures show that social impact analysis is not just theoretical; it is real and measurable.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="academic-success-scholarships-provided-by-universities-in-turkey">Academic Success Scholarships Provided by Universities in Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Academic scholarships are a lifeline for successful students who need financial support. Moreover, it is open not only for students who are not citizens of the Republic of Turkey, but also for anyone with global achievements.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="application-requirements-and-selection-process">Application Requirements and Selection Process</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In general, universities evaluate students based on special exams or past academic performance during the application period. For example, Boğaziçi University requires a GPA of at least 3.5/4 for undergraduate applications.</p>



<blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow">
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkish universities are creating equal opportunities for international students by providing detailed information about <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/turkiye-basari-burslari/" data-type="post" data-id="2502">academic merit scholarships</a>. These scholarships focus on leadership and social contribution, not just GPA.</p>
</blockquote>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="sports-scholarship-opportunities-and-application-requirements-in-turkey">Sports Scholarship Opportunities and Application Requirements in Turkey</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Sports scholarships are also quite common in Turkey and have a significant social impact.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="which-branches-are-given-scholarships">Which Branches Are Given Scholarships?</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Sports scholarships are generally available in the following areas:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Football</li>



<li>Basketball</li>



<li>Volleyball</li>



<li>Athletics</li>



<li>Individual sports like Taekwondo, Judo</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Universities that offer sports scholarships attach importance to the student being a licensed athlete and participating in competitions. Scholarship rates can vary between 25% and 100% depending on achievement.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="academic-and-social-success-of-athletic-students">Academic and Social Success of Athletic Students</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Students who play sports develop not only physically, but also in terms of social networks, leadership skills and self-confidence. This is where social impact analysis comes into play: Sports scholarships increase both the integration of students into campus life and their academic motivation.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="art-and-culture-scholarships-in-turkey-opportunities-and-criteria">Art and Culture Scholarships in Turkey: Opportunities and Criteria</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">When we think of arts scholarships, we immediately think of painting, music or theater, but in Turkey the concept is much broader. This type of scholarship, which is intertwined with cultural heritage, is a great opportunity both creatively and socially, especially for international students.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="supports-for-music-performing-arts-and-visual-arts">Supports for Music, Performing Arts and Visual Arts</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Institutions such as Yıldız Technical University, Mimar Sinan Fine Arts University and Hacettepe University stand out with their art and culture scholarships. Scholarships, in particular:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Conservatory students</li>



<li>Students of departments such as art, graphic design, interior architecture</li>



<li>Given to students who are active in the performing arts.</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Scholarships usually range between 100-150 USD per month, and students are also supported to participate in exhibitions, performances or competitions.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="cultural-diversity-and-international-contributions">Cultural Diversity and International Contributions</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">International students bring their culture to the university through the arts. This creates enrichment not only on campus, but also in society at large. This is where the <strong>social impact analysis</strong> of art scholarships paints a very powerful picture: Intercultural dialog is increasing and social awareness is strengthening.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="social-impact-of-scholarship-programs-on-international-students">Social Impact of Scholarship Programs on International Students</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">A student who is financially supported;</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Participates in social events</li>



<li>Participates in volunteer projects</li>



<li>Sustaining academic success</li>
</ul>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">This proves that in terms of <strong>social impact analysis</strong>, the scholarship affects not only the individual but also his/her environment.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="cultural-integration-and-language-development">Cultural Integration and Language Development</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Many scholarship programs include Turkish preparatory education. Language education facilitates social adaptation. The student both succeeds academically and integrates into society faster. We have also given important information about this in our detailed article on <a>student life</a>.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="shaping-the-future-in-light-of-social-impact-analysis">Shaping the Future in Light of Social Impact Analysis</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">The concept of &#8220;social impact analysis&#8221;, which we have repeatedly referred to in this article, should be placed at the center of education policies. Scholarship programs in Turkey make a significant contribution not only to the development of the individual but also to the development of society.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="the-contribution-of-scholarships-to-social-development">The Contribution of Scholarships to Social Development</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Social diversity and cultural cohesion on the rise</li>



<li>Academic success is spreading</li>



<li>Voluntary participation in social services on the rise</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="policy-recommendations-for-more-impact">Policy Recommendations for More Impact</h3>



<ol class="wp-block-list">
<li>Scholar tracking systems should be established</li>



<li>Develop support programs for graduates</li>



<li>Support projects that increase student interaction with the local community</li>



<li>Number and scope of scholarships should be expanded annually</li>
</ol>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">All of these steps enable scholarship systems to develop with a stronger <strong>social impact analysis</strong> infrastructure.</p>


<div style="height:23px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>
<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" >
<div style="height:24px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="education-with-scholarships-in-turkey-apply-now-make-a-difference">Education with Scholarships in Turkey: Apply Now, Make a Difference</h2>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">If you want to get the education of your dreams and transform your life, don&#8217;t miss this opportunity. Scholarships in Turkey offer a brand new life, not just a diploma.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="why-now-is-the-time-to-take-the-first-step">Why Now is the Time to Take the First Step</h3>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Applications start at this time of year and places fill up fast. Don&#8217;t let financial worries, social isolation or language barriers scare you. With the support provided by scholarship programs, these problems are eliminated.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2025-08-26T10:49:26Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-15T18:44:54Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/social-impact-analysis-of-scholarship-programs-in-turkey.webp","alt":"Two students sitting on the grass and talking, with a university building in the background.","title":"social-impact-analysis-of-scholarship-programs-in-turkey"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'turkey-scholarships-social-impact-analysis' );
